1.0.name: wordpress/catfish-ad-manager
1.0.description: The Catfish Manager allows you to setup and manage Catfish ads easily within WordPress. It was created by Matt Oakes with the aid of Nathan Allan. It allows for the easy inclusion of Catfish style ads on any WordPress site.
